"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1640088736,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"z3up8yK1i72IpL9WWzo9HWO_Mt87ok5IEAPIKQEA_zw\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x8CD42b2b022C53546aA64CE3613714D6c4081174\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ZrVz41DFBfMu_iAo77Q5tMlbtXu5a-357DjxX10k1_c\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"vx_jykEABlUngTpeXF_QTempvZyqDu3Cr0Ty64AoPzs\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"HAcGMqXq4zIrj5ojZ3KvoruO7DLmmxfmAR9Qhlp2OOo7K_dDi4Jbqkyf3bBs7_Akj2kY9-hJ4uR1-m2y61BNTQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xc7f23e094c7b869e91175b57482cab3cbdd2f671b07be96203449384a3a4669348bfc30199367eb270aa6b8c438cc3e6753b67655d91fca0c0af39ba4c1bdc381c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ZrVz41DFBfMu_iAo77Q5tMlbtXu5a-357DjxX10k1_c\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"vx_jykEABlUngTpeXF_QTempvZyqDu3Cr0Ty64AoPzs\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi